data.description: ***Lender Credit of $2,500 when using Carlo Colantonio with CMG Financial Home Loans (valid thru 12/31/23, can't be used with a bond or down payment assistance program, used towards closing costs)*** $5,000 Seller Closing Cost Assistance!! Welcome to resort living in the premier 55+ adult Hill Country Retreat by Del Webb located in the tranquil and scenic Alamo Ranch. Neighborhood entry offers controlled access for added peace and security. This delightful home offers an open floor plan, stunning stone fireplace, spacious master bedroom with a large master bathroom, craft room (can be used as a third bedroom), and a study/office. The garage offers overhead storage, full insulation, epoxy floors, mini-split AC, garage door opener, and a water softener. Relax on the large covered back patio with park-like views. There is nearby shopping and dining with easy access to Loop 1604.
